# HotelPhotoDto

Photos specific information of the hotel.

**Properties**

| Name        | Type    | Required | Description                                    |
| :---------- | :------ | :------- | :--------------------------------------------- |
| mainPhoto   | boolean | ❌       | Is this the main hotel photo.                  |
| urlOriginal | string  | ❌       | Url of the photo with max width of 500 pixels. |
